{"tid":1717820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致 各位核彈都唔割既手足 同前線勇武 想同大家講少少野","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T05:30:01.000Z","uid":38131,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fe29f349e038d659cec0f429377dfc0a14e1cc22","tid":1717820,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"如果你地想攬炒<br />\n無論前線一切行動做咩都唔割<br />\n咁點解唔燒哂巴士<br />\n唔炸哂全部變電站?<br />\n呢d攬炒行動更加快更加有效<br />\n<br />\n我相信大家冇咁做都係知道背後仲有道德底線<br />\n但而家愈畫愈後<br />\n真係好擔心...<br />\n又一次見到燒地鋪燒到好危險<br />\n真係好灰<br />\n我想大家認真檢討一下<br />\n放火燒藍絲鋪係唔係真係有成果<br />\n<br />\n各位記住核彈都唔割 背後仲有條道德底線係到<br />\n要控制情緒 <br />\n好唔好?"},{"pid":"496eae32492e17d6aace674b88b20cd4e5388311","tid":1717820,"uid":87123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c6827b2da91d2a58c9b81458918ccf32198ecba","tid":1717820,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1714238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1714238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb7597e64cb0ca450f2c7d570cedcbdc94ec9d51","tid":1717820,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"[和你勇文宣升級！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嬲好嬲好嬲，但文宣更要做好，要拉攏最多人過黎同對方憾過，我地從來都唔係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81d6c